channel.title: mycatalog updates
channel.description: 'My Catalog' uses the IBM Cloud catalog API to retrieve data from the catalog. It attempts to be as accurate as possible. This feed shows additions, updates, removals from the catalog. Use with care. It is a work-in-progress :)

item.title: [updated] NeuralSeek (neuralseek) has a new plan named neuralseek-small-business
item.description: The Small Business plan is the easiest way to start with NeuralSeek. This plan does not require an external knowledge base like Watson Discovery. Simply point NeuralSeek at your website or upload documents and everything else is handled for you.
